{"id":55,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":55,"title":"Chapter 51: The Jaredites Travel to the Promised Land","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 51","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 51"],["h1","The Jaredites Travel to the Promised Land"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p3"},"While the Jaredites camped by the sea, the brother of Jared forgot to pray. The Lord came in a cloud to tell him to repent."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.14"},"Ether 2:14"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p5"},"The brother of Jared repented and prayed. The Lord forgave the brother of Jared but said he should not sin anymore."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.15"},"Ether 2:15"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p7"},"The Lord told the brother of Jared to build barges to take his people to the promised land."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.16"},"Ether 2:16"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p9"},"The Lord told the brother of Jared how to build the barges."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.16-17"},"Ether 2:16–17"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p11"},"The barges were made airtight so no water could get inside."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.17"},"Ether 2:17"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p13"},"The brother of Jared wondered how the people would have air to breathe in the barges. He asked the Lord what he should do."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.19"},"Ether 2:19"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p15"},"The Lord told him to make a hole in the top and bottom of each barge. The hole could be opened to let air in and closed to keep water out."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.20"},"Ether 2:20"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p17"},"The brother of Jared told the Lord that the barges were dark inside. The Lord asked him to think of a way to have light inside the barges."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.22-23"},"Ether 2:22–23"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p19"},"The light for the barges could not come from fire or from windows because they would break."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/2.23"},"Ether 2:23"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p21"},"The brother of Jared went to a mountain and formed 16 small stones from a rock. The stones looked like clear glass. He made two stones for each of the eight barges."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/3.1"},"Ether 3:1"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p23"},"The brother of Jared carried the stones to the top of a mountain. There he prayed to the Lord."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/3.1"},"Ether 3:1"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f12"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_12.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p25","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p25"},"The brother of Jared asked the Lord to touch the stones so they would give light inside the barges."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p26","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p26"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/3.4"},"Ether 3:4"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f13"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_13.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p27","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p27"},"The Lord touched each stone with his finger."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p28","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p28"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/3.6"},"Ether 3:6"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f14"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_14.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p29","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p29"},"Because the brother of Jared had great faith, he saw the finger of the Lord. It looked like a human finger."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p30","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p30"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/3.6,9"},"Ether 3:6, 9"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f15"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_15.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p31","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p31"},"Then the Lord showed himself to the brother of Jared."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p32","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p32"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/3.13"},"Ether 3:13"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f16"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_16.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p33","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p33"},"Jesus said those people who believe in him will have eternal life."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p34","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p34"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/3.14"},"Ether 3:14"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f17"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_17.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p35","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p35"},"Jesus taught and showed the brother of Jared many things. Jesus told him to write what he had seen and heard."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p36","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p36"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/3.25-27"},"Ether 3:25–27"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f18"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_18.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p37","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p37"},"The brother of Jared carried the stones down the mountain. He put one stone in each end of each barge. They gave light inside the barges."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p38","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p38"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/6.2-3"},"Ether 6:2–3"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f19"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_19.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p39","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p39"},"The Jaredites went into the barges with their animals and food. The Lord made a strong wind blow the barges toward the promised land."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p40","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p40"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/6.4-5"},"Ether 6:4–5"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f20"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_20.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p41","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p41"},"The Lord protected them in the rough sea. They thanked the Lord and sang praises to him."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p42","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p42"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/6.6-10"},"Ether 6:6–10"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f21"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_21.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p43","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p43"},"After 344 days on the water, the barges landed on the shore of the promised land."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p44","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p44"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/6.11-12"},"Ether 6:11–12"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f22"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_22.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p45","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p45"},"When the Jaredites came out of the barges, they knelt down and cried tears of joy."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p46","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p46"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/6.12"},"Ether 6:12"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.f23"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_055_23.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p47","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p47"},"The Jaredites built homes and planted crops in the promised land. They taught their children to listen to the Lord and obey his words."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p48","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-51-the-jaredites-travel-to-the-promised-land.p48"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/6.13,16-18"},"Ether 6:13, 16–18"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
